item.title: Blanco Brown - The Git Up
item.description:
The Git Up by Blanco Brown. It’s been lowered by 2 semitones to the key of D so beginner BARITONE ukulele can play along. For educational use. Chords Used: D & G
If you found this video useful please subscribe. If you want to be notified of future videos please click on bell next to subscribe.
